 App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwjRhMLEt-uTAxWlyJUCHZtAB-ZI99jmjIy1yeAIygEE4PYAuw==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbG90aVJjSzYzbmpscGdJRmpHWTRZdDhWUFJNd3xBQ3Jtc0ttZGRHaU55R0lyMkZTWTJveU5nYTJrZHpFU0oxQ2RJLWM3WDJmYXBXTXJJRTRYOTFVY0JPYm9xdko3ODJ5a01US1Fsek5ZUTFjd19qYmVhRUNULUk0ZENMZHVPeEIyMlZ5QnhrRmJLSXc0UDBLU0RNSQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=CMElqMGZrHc","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbG90aVJjSzYzbmpscGdJRmpHWTRZdDhWUFJNd3xBQ3Jtc0ttZGRHaU55R0lyMkZTWTJveU5nYTJrZHpFU0oxQ2RJLWM3WDJmYXBXTXJJRTRYOTFVY0JPYm9xdko3ODJ5a01US1Fsek5ZUTFjd19qYmVhRUNULUk0ZENMZHVPeEIyMlZ5QnhrRmJLSXc0UDBLU0RNSQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=CMElqMGZrHc","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwjRhMLEt-uTAxWlyJUCHZtAB-ZI99jmjIy1yeAIygEE4PYAuw==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbjZYclRyX2NMa3F5eFhrVUtKQUZQRDNVQXpxUXxBQ3Jtc0ttYkw1WTdGUnFhZUJFTWt0Z0hPZEVXVGh2QTRQUlZIQjNkQXJLc05PTXJQa21hdDRzRGZKUHplYTg1em8wWi0tR25JdnpRS0RUZmVPUjN5ZGlLV0